WEBVTT

00:04.360 --> 00:05.839
<font color="#ffffff">LUCY SCREAMS</font>

00:05.840 --> 00:07.640
<font color="#ffffff">It's OK!</font>

00:09.160 --> 00:10.919
<font color="#ffffff">I'm fine.</font>

00:10.920 --> 00:12.479
<font color="#ffff00">I was just worried you hadn't signed</font>

00:12.480 --> 00:14.000
<font color="#ffff00">the life insurance documents yet.</font>

00:14.856 --> 00:16.855
<font color="#ffffff">I was just sweeping up some bits.</font>

00:16.856 --> 00:18.695
<font color="#ffffff">I'm afraid your blue vase</font>
<font color="#ffffff">has broken.</font>

00:18.696 --> 00:21.136
<font color="#ffffff">SHE SCREAMS EVEN LOUDER</font>

00:23.576 --> 00:25.335
<font color="#ffffff"># We're not going out</font>

00:25.336 --> 00:27.175
<font color="#ffffff"># Not staying in</font>

00:27.176 --> 00:30.175
<font color="#ffffff"># Just hanging around</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with my head in a spin</font>

00:30.176 --> 00:33.055
<font color="#ffffff"># But there is no need to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">scream and shout</font>

00:33.056 --> 00:36.175
<font color="#ffffff"># We're not going out</font>

00:36.176 --> 00:39.136
<font color="#ffffff"># We are not going out. #</font>

00:42.376 --> 00:44.496
<font color="#ffffff">KNOCK AT THE DOOR</font>

00:48.296 --> 00:50.415
<font color="#ffff00">Oh! Hello.</font>

00:50.416 --> 00:52.975
<font color="#00ffff">Perhaps you could explain</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what this is all about.</font>

00:52.976 --> 00:54.335
<font color="#ffff00">What?</font>

00:54.336 --> 00:56.615
<font color="#00ffff">Why are we standing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at your front door?</font>

00:56.616 --> 00:59.655
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, dear. Is this like when Grandad</font>
<font color="#ffff00">used to turn up at Blockbusters</font>

00:59.656 --> 01:00.936
<font color="#ffff00">in a nightie?</font>

01:02.176 --> 01:04.334
<font color="#00ff00">Lee sent us a text message</font>
<font color="#00ff00">saying we had to come</font>

01:04.336 --> 01:05.775
<font color="#00ff00">round here immediately.</font>

01:05.776 --> 01:08.815
<font color="#ffff00">Did he?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Said it was extremely important.</font>

01:08.816 --> 01:11.695
<font color="#00ff00">We thought maybe you had</font>
<font color="#00ff00">some happy news to announce.</font>

01:11.696 --> 01:13.455
<font color="#ffff00">What, pregnancy?</font>

01:13.456 --> 01:14.736
<font color="#00ffff">Or divorce.</font>

01:15.896 --> 01:18.575
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, sorry to disappoint you, Dad,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">but it's neither.</font>

01:18.576 --> 01:22.495
<font color="#00ff00">Aw, so we won't be hearing</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the patter of tiny feet?</font>

01:22.496 --> 01:23.655
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, I don't know.</font>

01:23.656 --> 01:25.096
<font color="#ffff00">What's going on?</font>

01:27.096 --> 01:29.855
<font color="#ffff00">I've had a message off Lee telling</font>
<font color="#ffff00">me to get round here straight away.</font>

01:29.856 --> 01:31.535
<font color="#ffff00">Sounded urgent.</font>

01:31.536 --> 01:33.855
<font color="#00ffff">Well, they're not emptying out</font>
<font color="#00ffff">their drinks cabinet, Frank.</font>

01:33.856 --> 01:35.016
<font color="#00ffff">You can stand down.</font>

01:36.056 --> 01:38.095
<font color="#ffff00">I thought he might want help</font>
<font color="#ffff00">moving an old antique</font>

01:38.096 --> 01:40.096
<font color="#ffff00">that's blocking the doorway.</font>

01:41.896 --> 01:43.295
<font color="#ffffff">LUCY: </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh, don't tell me,</font>

01:43.296 --> 01:45.375
<font color="#ffff00">you got a text message</font>
<font color="#ffff00">from Lee telling you to get</font>

01:45.376 --> 01:46.615
<font color="#ffff00">round here urgently?</font>

01:46.616 --> 01:48.135
<font color="#00ffff">Yes, but we can't stay long.</font>

01:48.136 --> 01:49.735
<font color="#00ffff">I'm supposed to be packing.</font>

01:49.736 --> 01:51.376
<font color="#ffff00">She's finally leaving you, Toby?</font>

01:52.576 --> 01:54.295
<font color="#00ffff">We're going... </font><font color="#00ff00">Hang on.</font>

01:54.296 --> 01:55.936
<font color="#00ff00">Let's enjoy that a little longer.</font>

01:57.496 --> 01:59.855
<font color="#00ffff">We're going to my sister's</font>
<font color="#00ffff">first thing in the morning</font>

01:59.856 --> 02:02.455
<font color="#00ffff">so we really do need to make this</font>
<font color="#00ffff">quick. </font><font color="#00ff00">Us, too.</font>

02:02.456 --> 02:04.935
<font color="#00ff00">I've got a bag of trophies here</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for this evening's</font>

02:04.936 --> 02:06.535
<font color="#00ff00">golf club presentation.</font>

02:06.536 --> 02:08.975
<font color="#00ffff">Why didn't you leave them</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in the car?</font>

02:08.976 --> 02:10.574
<font color="#00ff00">Because they might get stolen.</font>

02:10.576 --> 02:12.975
<font color="#ffff00">Worth a bob or two, are they?</font>

02:12.976 --> 02:16.375
<font color="#00ff00">On second thoughts, perhaps I should</font>
<font color="#00ff00">have left them in the car.</font>

02:16.376 --> 02:18.336
<font color="#ffffff">Don't worry, this won't take long.</font>

02:19.736 --> 02:22.015
<font color="#ffffff">Good evening, one and all.</font>

02:22.016 --> 02:24.615
<font color="#ffffff">I suspect you're wondering why</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I've gathered you here tonight.</font>

02:24.616 --> 02:26.575
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, we certainly are, Poirot.</font>

02:26.576 --> 02:28.616
<font color="#ffff00">Looks more like Hetty Wainthropp.</font>

02:30.096 --> 02:32.735
<font color="#ffffff">Somebody here has committed a murder</font>

02:32.736 --> 02:35.575
<font color="#ffffff">and until we find out who it was...</font>

02:35.576 --> 02:37.455
<font color="#ffffff">..nobody...</font>

02:37.456 --> 02:39.255
<font color="#ffffff">..is going home.</font>

02:39.256 --> 02:40.296
<font color="#00ff00">It was me.</font>

02:41.936 --> 02:44.015
<font color="#ffffff">Do you know what I'm on about?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">No idea.</font>

02:44.016 --> 02:46.536
<font color="#00ff00">It's just my default position,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">taking the blame for everything.</font>

02:47.976 --> 02:50.055
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell are you talking about,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Lee?</font>

02:50.056 --> 02:52.495
<font color="#ffffff">Somebody here has killed something.</font>

02:52.496 --> 02:54.535
<font color="#ffffff">Should I tell you what</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that something is?</font>

02:54.536 --> 02:56.695
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, but can you say it really</font>
<font color="#00ff00">dramatically</font>

02:56.696 --> 02:58.256
<font color="#00ff00">and fully milk the moment?</font>

02:59.376 --> 03:01.655
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, no, wait, you have.</font>

03:01.656 --> 03:03.015
<font color="#ffffff">The something in question</font>

03:03.016 --> 03:05.335
<font color="#ffffff">is the trust that my darling wife</font>

03:05.336 --> 03:06.575
<font color="#ffffff">has in me.</font>

03:06.576 --> 03:09.175
<font color="#00ffff">So nobody has actually been</font>
<font color="#00ffff">murdered? </font><font color="#ffffff">'Course not.</font>

03:09.176 --> 03:11.416
<font color="#00ff00">Well, I don't know.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">The night is young.</font>

03:12.696 --> 03:13.935
<font color="#ffff00">I see.</font>

03:13.936 --> 03:15.975
<font color="#ffff00">So, you're still pretending it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">wasn't you, then?</font>

03:15.976 --> 03:18.295
<font color="#ffffff">I'm not pretending. It wasn't me.</font>

03:18.296 --> 03:20.015
<font color="#ffffff">It was somebody in this room!</font>

03:20.016 --> 03:21.215
<font color="#ffff00">Yes.</font>

03:21.216 --> 03:22.455
<font color="#ffff00">You.</font>

03:22.456 --> 03:23.855
<font color="#ffff00">And if you go into the kitchen,</font>

03:23.856 --> 03:25.856
<font color="#ffff00">it'll be somebody in the kitchen.</font>

03:26.976 --> 03:28.535
<font color="#00ffff">What on Earth is this about?</font>

03:28.536 --> 03:30.295
<font color="#00ffff">We really do need to get going.</font>

03:30.296 --> 03:32.895
<font color="#ffffff">Perhaps you'd like to fill</font>
<font color="#ffffff">everybody in, Lucy.</font>

03:32.896 --> 03:36.215
<font color="#ffff00">You know my blue and white vase?</font>

03:36.216 --> 03:37.775
<font color="#ffff00">The one that used to belong to Nan?</font>

03:37.776 --> 03:38.935
<font color="#00ff00">Ugly old thing.</font>

03:38.936 --> 03:40.535
<font color="#00ff00">Didn't hold water properly.</font>

03:40.536 --> 03:41.856
<font color="#00ff00">Don't!</font>

03:47.736 --> 03:50.335
<font color="#00ff00">I remember mother giving it to you.</font>

03:50.336 --> 03:52.936
<font color="#ffff00">Not much of a family heirloom.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">A vase?!</font>

03:54.056 --> 03:56.455
<font color="#00ff00">Well, it's amazing what silly</font>
<font color="#00ff00">little things people pass</font>

03:56.456 --> 03:57.935
<font color="#00ff00">on from generation to generation.</font>

03:57.936 --> 03:59.575
<font color="#00ff00">Some people have vases.</font>

03:59.576 --> 04:01.136
<font color="#00ff00">Some have alcoholism.</font>

04:02.936 --> 04:05.375
<font color="#ffff00">To be honest, it was hidden away</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for years.</font>

04:05.376 --> 04:07.935
<font color="#00ff00">Yeah, a bit like alcoholism.</font>

04:07.936 --> 04:10.815
<font color="#ffff00">Recently I got it out again,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and when I came home today,</font>

04:10.816 --> 04:14.215
<font color="#ffff00">it was lying on the floor,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">completely smashed.</font>

04:14.216 --> 04:16.736
<font color="#00ff00">Well, the similarities keep on</font>
<font color="#00ff00">coming. Don't they, Frank?</font>

04:18.736 --> 04:20.935
<font color="#00ffff">Are you sure the children</font>
<font color="#00ffff">didn't break it?</font>

04:20.935 --> 04:24.495
<font color="#ffff00">They were out of the house</font>
<font color="#ffff00">all day with me.</font>

04:24.496 --> 04:26.855
<font color="#ffff00">It could only have been Lee.</font>

04:26.856 --> 04:29.095
<font color="#ffff00">I don't think it had much monetary</font>
<font color="#ffff00">value but it had</font>

04:29.096 --> 04:30.855
<font color="#ffff00">lots of sentimental value.</font>

04:30.856 --> 04:32.415
<font color="#ffff00">It was my nan's.</font>

04:32.416 --> 04:34.655
<font color="#00ffff">I'm sorry about your vase, Lucy,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I really am,</font>

04:34.656 --> 04:36.855
<font color="#00ffff">but what the hell has this got to do</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with any of us?</font>

04:36.856 --> 04:38.816
<font color="#ffffff">Please allow me to explain.</font>

04:40.216 --> 04:43.655
<font color="#ffffff">I came home from work today, five</font>
<font color="#ffffff">minutes before Lucy, to find a vase</font>

04:43.656 --> 04:45.695
<font color="#ffffff">of flowers smashed on the floor.</font>

04:45.696 --> 04:49.335
<font color="#ffffff">Naturally, I went into the kitchen</font>
<font color="#ffffff">to get a dustpan and brush to sweep</font>

04:49.336 --> 04:51.855
<font color="#ffffff">it up and that's when Lucy entered.</font>

04:51.856 --> 04:53.496
<font color="#00ff00">This is gripping stuff.</font>

04:55.136 --> 04:59.495
<font color="#00ff00">Let's hope Meryl Streep is available</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for the Crimewatch reconstruction.</font>

04:59.496 --> 05:02.935
<font color="#ffffff">And that's when Lucy accused me of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">breaking it.</font>

05:02.936 --> 05:06.535
<font color="#ffffff">She berated me and threatened me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">with all kinds of punishment.</font>

05:06.536 --> 05:07.855
<font color="#ffff00">No, I didn't!</font>

05:07.856 --> 05:11.095
<font color="#ffffff">You said our usual Fruity Friday</font>
<font color="#ffffff">was cancelled.</font>

05:11.096 --> 05:12.375
<font color="#00ffff">Fruity...?</font>

05:12.376 --> 05:15.136
<font color="#00ff00">If it means they're getting</font>
<font color="#00ff00">five a day, I'm impressed.</font>

05:18.096 --> 05:20.055
<font color="#ffffff">But then, afterwards,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">it got me thinking.</font>

05:20.056 --> 05:22.655
<font color="#ffffff">"Hang on, I've actually got proof</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that it wasn't me!"</font>

05:22.656 --> 05:23.975
<font color="#ffff00">What proof?</font>

05:23.976 --> 05:27.095
<font color="#ffffff">If I had broken that vase</font>
<font color="#ffffff">five minutes before you came in,</font>

05:27.096 --> 05:30.055
<font color="#ffffff">why wasn't the rug still wet?</font>

05:30.056 --> 05:32.655
<font color="#ffffff">In fact, given it's now only 6:15,</font>

05:32.656 --> 05:35.216
<font color="#ffffff">you'd expect it to be a little bit</font>
<font color="#ffffff">damp now, right?</font>

05:38.256 --> 05:39.615
<font color="#ffff00">It's bone dry.</font>

05:39.616 --> 05:41.135
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, very clever, Lee.</font>

05:41.136 --> 05:42.255
<font color="#00ff00">Yes.</font>

05:42.256 --> 05:44.736
<font color="#00ff00">Like when a monkey completes</font>
<font color="#00ff00">a two-piece jigsaw.</font>

05:46.776 --> 05:49.935
<font color="#ffffff">Which means somebody else must have</font>
<font color="#ffffff">broken that vase earlier</font>

05:49.936 --> 05:51.975
<font color="#ffffff">in the day whilst I was at work.</font>

05:51.976 --> 05:55.055
<font color="#ffffff">And who are the only other people</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that know where we hide the spare</font>

05:55.056 --> 05:57.735
<font color="#ffffff">key for the house?</font>

05:57.736 --> 05:58.896
<font color="#ffffff">You lot.</font>

06:00.416 --> 06:03.015
<font color="#00ffff">I can't believe we've been dragged</font>
<font color="#00ffff">all the way over here</font>

06:03.016 --> 06:05.375
<font color="#00ffff">just because of a petty</font>
<font color="#00ffff">domestic squabble.</font>

06:05.376 --> 06:07.776
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, we could have stayed at home</font>
<font color="#00ff00">for one of those.</font>

06:09.016 --> 06:10.696
<font color="#00ffff">This is ridiculous!</font>

06:11.936 --> 06:13.335
<font color="#00ffff">I never liked that vase, anyway.</font>

06:13.336 --> 06:14.735
<font color="#00ffff">We're leaving.</font>

06:14.736 --> 06:18.775
<font color="#ffffff">Nobody leaves until I find out</font>
<font color="#ffffff">who's sullied my good name</font>

06:18.776 --> 06:20.295
<font color="#ffffff">and besmirched my reputation.</font>

06:20.296 --> 06:24.255
<font color="#00ff00">Have you considered that perhaps</font>
<font color="#00ff00">nobody broke it?</font>

06:24.256 --> 06:26.455
<font color="#00ff00">This table is very wobbly.</font>

06:26.456 --> 06:29.175
<font color="#00ffff">You need to put a folded beermat</font>
<font color="#00ffff">under there.</font>

06:29.176 --> 06:30.495
<font color="#00ff00">Bravo, Frank.</font>

06:30.496 --> 06:32.456
<font color="#00ff00">Wetherspoon's answer to Bear Grylls.</font>

06:34.376 --> 06:36.175
<font color="#00ff00">Open that door. </font><font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

06:36.176 --> 06:37.455
<font color="#00ffff">This is ridiculous.</font>

06:37.456 --> 06:40.135
<font color="#00ffff">You could easily have smashed that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">vase of lilies and then quickly</font>

06:40.136 --> 06:42.336
<font color="#00ffff">thrown the rug into</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the tumble dryer.</font>

06:44.256 --> 06:46.535
<font color="#ffff00">How did you know they were lilies,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Mum?</font>

06:46.536 --> 06:48.095
<font color="#00ffff">You said they were lilies.</font>

06:48.096 --> 06:49.775
<font color="#ffffff">No, she didn't.</font>

06:49.776 --> 06:51.775
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, this is nonsense!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">We've got to go,</font>

06:51.776 --> 06:53.775
<font color="#00ffff">we need to get to that golf club</font>
<font color="#00ffff">function.</font>

06:53.776 --> 06:56.175
<font color="#ffffff">Well, nobody else is in a rush.</font>

06:56.176 --> 06:58.856
<font color="#ffffff">Are you? </font><font color="#ffff00">No, I haven't got</font>
<font color="#ffff00">a function.</font>

06:59.936 --> 07:02.895
<font color="#00ff00">That's true on so many levels.</font>

07:02.896 --> 07:05.855
<font color="#00ffff">I must have seen the lilies</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in the vase when we were all</font>

07:05.856 --> 07:07.335
<font color="#00ffff">round here for dinner the other day.</font>

07:07.336 --> 07:08.495
<font color="#00ffff">You remember.</font>

07:08.496 --> 07:10.655
<font color="#00ff00">Well, actually,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I was rather preoccupied</font>

07:10.656 --> 07:13.935
<font color="#00ff00">watching Frank get to grips</font>
<font color="#00ff00">with the concept of cutlery.</font>

07:13.936 --> 07:16.495
<font color="#ffff00">But I only put the flowers</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in the vase last night.</font>

07:16.496 --> 07:18.535
<font color="#ffffff">So, how did you know they were</font>
<font color="#ffffff">lilies?</font>

07:18.536 --> 07:20.535
<font color="#00ffff">All right, yes, I admit it.</font>

07:20.536 --> 07:22.175
<font color="#00ffff">I came around here this morning.</font>

07:22.176 --> 07:23.535
<font color="#ffffff">I knew it!</font>

07:23.536 --> 07:24.575
<font color="#ffff00">Mum!</font>

07:24.576 --> 07:26.495
<font color="#00ffff">It's not that unusual!</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I often pop round here</font>

07:26.496 --> 07:28.215
<font color="#00ffff">to do the odd errand or two,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you know that.</font>

07:28.216 --> 07:29.895
<font color="#ffff00">But why didn't you say something?</font>

07:29.896 --> 07:32.615
<font color="#00ffff">I don't tell you about</font>
<font color="#00ffff">every little thing I do.</font>

07:32.616 --> 07:34.815
<font color="#ffff00">Mum, last week you rang me to say</font>

07:34.816 --> 07:37.455
<font color="#ffff00">they'd moved the tinfoil</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in Waitrose!</font>

07:37.456 --> 07:40.095
<font color="#ffffff">I think we are waiting</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for an explanation, Wendy.</font>

07:40.096 --> 07:42.376
<font color="#00ffff">They did it to make room</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for the bin liners.</font>

07:44.256 --> 07:45.655
<font color="#00ff00">Hang on.</font>

07:45.656 --> 07:47.295
<font color="#00ff00">Is this what I think it's about?</font>

07:47.296 --> 07:48.975
<font color="#00ffff">Yes. </font><font color="#00ff00">Oh, for God's sake!</font>

07:48.976 --> 07:50.455
<font color="#00ff00">I told you to drop this!</font>

07:50.456 --> 07:51.695
<font color="#ffff00">What?</font>

07:51.696 --> 07:53.375
<font color="#00ffff">It started last weekend.</font>

07:53.376 --> 07:57.456
<font color="#00ffff">Geoffrey and I were at home watching</font>
<font color="#00ffff">an episode of the Antiques Roadshow.</font>

07:58.776 --> 08:01.015
<font color="#00ffff">There was a person on there</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with a vase.</font>

08:01.016 --> 08:04.095
<font color="#ffffff">A vase? </font><font color="#00ffff">A blue and white vase that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">looked exactly</font>

08:04.096 --> 08:05.375
<font color="#00ffff">the same as Lucy's.</font>

08:05.376 --> 08:06.815
<font color="#ffffff">Well, how much was it worth?</font>

08:06.816 --> 08:08.496
<font color="#00ffff">£2,000.</font>

08:10.056 --> 08:11.495
<font color="#ffff00">Well, why didn't you tell me?</font>

08:11.496 --> 08:14.735
<font color="#00ffff">I wanted to! In fact, I picked up</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the phone immediately to call you.</font>

08:14.736 --> 08:16.215
<font color="#00ff00">But I told her not to do it.</font>

08:16.216 --> 08:17.375
<font color="#ffff00">Why?</font>

08:17.376 --> 08:18.575
<font color="#00ff00">Because, as the expert said,</font>

08:18.576 --> 08:20.535
<font color="#00ff00">there are thousands of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">similar-looking vases</font>

08:20.536 --> 08:22.415
<font color="#00ff00">in charity shops up and down</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the country</font>

08:22.416 --> 08:23.935
<font color="#00ff00">that are all totally worthless.</font>

08:23.936 --> 08:26.535
<font color="#00ffff">Well, they certainly know what</font>
<font color="#00ffff">they're talking about on that show.</font>

08:26.536 --> 08:29.815
<font color="#00ff00">Exactly! And Lucy's was almost</font>
<font color="#00ff00">certainly one of the worthless ones.</font>

08:29.816 --> 08:31.696
<font color="#ffff00">Well, it is now, anyway.</font>

08:32.895 --> 08:34.895
<font color="#00ff00">If we'd told you, Lucy,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you'd have got all excited</font>

08:34.895 --> 08:37.655
<font color="#00ff00">and gone round to an antiques dealer</font>
<font color="#00ff00">and then you'd have been made to</font>

08:37.655 --> 08:39.975
<font color="#00ff00">look a fool when he told you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">it was only worth pennies.</font>

08:39.976 --> 08:41.534
<font color="#ffff00">And you agreed with him, Mum?</font>

08:41.535 --> 08:43.174
<font color="#00ffff">I could see your dad had a point.</font>

08:43.176 --> 08:45.655
<font color="#00ffff">I didn't want your hopes raised</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for nothing.</font>

08:45.656 --> 08:49.535
<font color="#00ffff">But I couldn't shake the idea that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">your vase just might be valuable.</font>

08:49.536 --> 08:51.455
<font color="#00ffff">And that's why,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">without your dad knowing,</font>

08:51.456 --> 08:53.335
<font color="#00ffff">I came round here this morning.</font>

08:53.336 --> 08:55.095
<font color="#ffffff">And accidentally broke it.</font>

08:55.096 --> 08:58.615
<font color="#00ffff">I just borrowed it for half an hour</font>
<font color="#00ffff">so I could take it to a dealer!</font>

08:58.616 --> 09:00.055
<font color="#ffffff">OK.</font>

09:00.056 --> 09:01.535
<font color="#ffffff">So, you borrowed it.</font>

09:01.536 --> 09:03.936
<font color="#ffffff">You took it off to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">"We Buy Any Vase dot com".</font>

09:05.696 --> 09:07.255
<font color="#ffffff">The big question is...</font>

09:07.256 --> 09:08.775
<font color="#ffffff">..how much was it worth?</font>

09:08.776 --> 09:11.215
<font color="#00ffff">Absolutely nothing.</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Geoffrey was right.</font>

09:11.216 --> 09:14.095
<font color="#00ffff">It was just a cheap replica</font>
<font color="#00ffff">after all. </font><font color="#00ff00">I knew it.</font>

09:14.096 --> 09:15.495
<font color="#00ffff">No harm done, then.</font>

09:15.496 --> 09:17.335
<font color="#00ffff">Just an ugly, cheap vase.</font>

09:17.336 --> 09:20.175
<font color="#ffff00">That Nan gave me</font>
<font color="#ffff00">and that someone has broken!</font>

09:20.176 --> 09:21.535
<font color="#00ffff">Well, it wasn't me!</font>

09:21.536 --> 09:23.655
<font color="#ffffff">Well, who was it?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">The antiques dealer?</font>

09:23.656 --> 09:26.295
<font color="#00ffff">What kind of antiques dealer</font>
<font color="#00ffff">smashes things?</font>

09:26.296 --> 09:27.616
<font color="#00ff00">A broker?</font>

09:30.656 --> 09:31.896
<font color="#00ff00">Too soon?</font>

09:33.296 --> 09:35.415
<font color="#00ffff">After I had it valued,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I came back here,</font>

09:35.416 --> 09:38.935
<font color="#00ffff">I refilled it with water, replaced</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the lilies, put it back exactly</font>

09:38.936 --> 09:41.095
<font color="#00ffff">where I found it and left.</font>

09:41.096 --> 09:42.816
<font color="#00ffff">I didn't break anything.</font>

09:44.176 --> 09:46.375
<font color="#00ffff">I feel everyone's turned on me.</font>

09:46.376 --> 09:47.895
<font color="#ffff00">Don't worry, Wendy.</font>

09:47.896 --> 09:49.655
<font color="#ffff00">I believe you.</font>

09:49.656 --> 09:52.016
<font color="#ffff00">I don't want you to feel turned on</font>
<font color="#ffff00">because of me.</font>

09:55.056 --> 09:58.375
<font color="#00ffff">Look, I didn't want to get involved</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in a family dispute</font>

09:58.376 --> 10:01.215
<font color="#00ffff">but I don't think it's fair that</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Wendy is the only one</font>

10:01.216 --> 10:03.175
<font color="#00ffff">having the finger pointed at her.</font>

10:03.176 --> 10:05.895
<font color="#00ffff">I drove past the house</font>
<font color="#00ffff">this lunchtime...</font>

10:05.896 --> 10:07.976
<font color="#00ffff">..and I saw Frank coming out.</font>

10:09.616 --> 10:10.975
<font color="#ffff00">You couldn't have seen me!</font>

10:10.976 --> 10:12.455
<font color="#00ff00">Why not?</font>

10:12.456 --> 10:14.896
<font color="#ffff00">Because I made sure there wasn't</font>
<font color="#ffff00">anyone watching.</font>

10:17.016 --> 10:18.735
<font color="#ffff00">All right.</font>

10:18.736 --> 10:20.735
<font color="#ffff00">I was here.</font>

10:20.736 --> 10:23.535
<font color="#ffff00">I wanted to find out if Wendy took</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the vase to be valued or not.</font>

10:23.536 --> 10:26.455
<font color="#ffffff">Well, how did you know about that?</font>

10:26.456 --> 10:28.375
<font color="#00ffff">May as well tell the truth.</font>

10:28.376 --> 10:30.735
<font color="#00ffff">Frank and I are in this together.</font>

10:30.736 --> 10:32.096
<font color="#00ff00">What?!</font>

10:33.656 --> 10:35.895
<font color="#00ffff">When we were all round here</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for dinner the other day,</font>

10:35.896 --> 10:37.895
<font color="#00ffff">I happened to mention to Frank</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about the vase</font>

10:37.896 --> 10:40.015
<font color="#00ffff">I'd seen on the Antiques Roadshow.</font>

10:40.016 --> 10:42.215
<font color="#ffffff">LUCY: </font><font color="#ffff00">And still no-one thought to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">say anything to me?</font>

10:42.216 --> 10:44.215
<font color="#ffff00">Anything else you've kept from me?</font>

10:44.216 --> 10:45.575
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, now you mentioned it,</font>

10:45.576 --> 10:48.656
<font color="#00ff00">you know when you asked was your</font>
<font color="#00ff00">beef a little overcooked?</font>

10:50.136 --> 10:51.656
<font color="#ffffff">Was that beef?!</font>

10:54.376 --> 10:57.215
<font color="#00ffff">I told Frank that Geoffrey thought</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it was pointless getting it valued.</font>

10:57.216 --> 10:59.415
<font color="#00ffff">But Frank agreed with me</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that I should!</font>

10:59.416 --> 11:03.135
<font color="#00ff00">So, not only did you go behind</font>
<font color="#00ff00">my back,</font>

11:03.136 --> 11:05.415
<font color="#00ff00">you went behind my back with him!</font>

11:05.416 --> 11:07.976
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry you should hear it</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like this, Geoffrey, but...</font>

11:09.336 --> 11:11.216
<font color="#ffff00">..Wendy and I are lovers.</font>

11:15.136 --> 11:16.536
<font color="#ffff00">Lovers of antiques.</font>

11:17.696 --> 11:19.135
<font color="#ffffff">Someone sleeping with you, Dad,</font>

11:19.136 --> 11:20.616
<font color="#ffffff">it's the same thing.</font>

11:21.936 --> 11:23.695
<font color="#00ffff">Frank was very helpful, actually.</font>

11:23.696 --> 11:25.975
<font color="#00ffff">He recommended someone who deals</font>
<font color="#00ffff">in antiques.</font>

11:25.976 --> 11:27.615
<font color="#00ffff">A friend of his.</font>

11:27.616 --> 11:29.095
<font color="#ffffff">Hang on.</font>

11:29.096 --> 11:33.255
<font color="#ffffff">You told my dad you thought</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Lucy owned a valuable vase</font>

11:33.256 --> 11:37.775
<font color="#ffffff">and he suddenly recommended you go</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and see one of his mates?</font>

11:37.776 --> 11:39.055
<font color="#00ffff">That's right.</font>

11:39.056 --> 11:41.575
<font color="#ffffff">Am I right in assuming this person</font>
<font color="#ffffff">wasn't chief auctioneer</font>

11:41.576 --> 11:42.736
<font color="#ffffff">at Sotheby's?</font>

11:44.456 --> 11:46.055
<font color="#00ffff">But he seemed very knowledgeable.</font>

11:46.056 --> 11:47.775
<font color="#ffffff">What kind of shop did he have?</font>

11:47.776 --> 11:48.935
<font color="#00ffff">It wasn't a shop,</font>

11:48.936 --> 11:50.976
<font color="#00ffff">more a sort of lock-up garage.</font>

11:52.216 --> 11:54.855
<font color="#00ffff">But he must've had some valuable</font>
<font color="#00ffff">pieces there or there'd have been</font>

11:54.856 --> 11:56.256
<font color="#00ffff">no need for all the dogs!</font>

11:58.576 --> 12:01.255
<font color="#ffffff">Can no-one else see</font>
<font color="#ffffff">what's going on here? </font><font color="#ffff00">What?</font>

12:01.256 --> 12:04.775
<font color="#00ff00">Well, he's suggesting that Frank's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">associate deliberately undervalued</font>

12:04.776 --> 12:07.335
<font color="#00ff00">the vase so that Frank could come</font>
<font color="#00ff00">round here,</font>

12:07.336 --> 12:11.855
<font color="#00ff00">take it and then he and his friend</font>
<font color="#00ff00">could split the profits.</font>

12:11.856 --> 12:14.895
<font color="#ffff00">I have never been so insulted</font>
<font color="#ffff00">in my life.</font>

12:14.896 --> 12:17.016
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, stick around, Dad.</font>

12:18.456 --> 12:19.815
<font color="#ffffff">What happened?</font>

12:19.816 --> 12:22.455
<font color="#ffffff">Did your plan go wrong</font>
<font color="#ffffff">when you accidently broke it?</font>

12:22.456 --> 12:23.816
<font color="#ffff00">Well...</font>

12:25.096 --> 12:27.535
<font color="#ffff00">..I can see you've all made</font>
<font color="#ffff00">your minds up.</font>

12:27.536 --> 12:29.935
<font color="#ffff00">You've convicted me and thrown away</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the keys.</font>

12:29.936 --> 12:32.855
<font color="#00ffff">Well, anyway, it looks like</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the mystery has been solved.</font>

12:32.856 --> 12:34.415
<font color="#ffff00">No, it bloody hasn't!</font>

12:34.416 --> 12:36.015
<font color="#00ff00">We really need to get going.</font>

12:36.016 --> 12:37.295
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

12:37.296 --> 12:39.655
<font color="#00ffff">We're making an early start</font>
<font color="#00ffff">for Woodcombe in the morning.</font>

12:39.656 --> 12:41.095
<font color="#00ffff">My sister hates us being late.</font>

12:41.096 --> 12:43.775
<font color="#ffff00">I'm sorry, Woodcombe?</font>

12:43.776 --> 12:46.775
<font color="#00ff00">Yes, in Somerset.</font>
<font color="#00ff00">It's where Anna's sister lives.</font>

12:46.776 --> 12:48.455
<font color="#ffff00">That's a coincidence, Hannah.</font>

12:48.456 --> 12:50.775
<font color="#ffff00">That's the place where they filmed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the episode</font>

12:50.776 --> 12:52.495
<font color="#ffff00">of Antiques Roadshow we watched.</font>

12:52.496 --> 12:54.095
<font color="#00ffff">Oh.</font>

12:54.096 --> 12:55.615
<font color="#00ffff">Really?</font>

12:55.616 --> 12:57.935
<font color="#ffff00">I'm surprised your sister didn't</font>
<font color="#ffff00">mention it to you.</font>

12:57.936 --> 13:00.015
<font color="#00ffff">Well, she probably didn't hear</font>
<font color="#00ffff">about it.</font>

13:00.016 --> 13:01.295
<font color="#00ffff">It's a very big town.</font>

13:01.296 --> 13:03.975
<font color="#ffff00">Fiona Bruce said only 200 people</font>
<font color="#ffff00">live there.</font>

13:03.976 --> 13:05.735
<font color="#00ffff">Did she?</font>

13:05.736 --> 13:09.135
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, I wouldn't know, I've never</font>
<font color="#00ffff">watched the Antiques Roadshow.</font>

13:09.136 --> 13:11.935
<font color="#00ffff">If I want to see someone have a</font>
<font color="#00ffff">heart attack when they find out</font>

13:11.936 --> 13:14.415
<font color="#00ffff">the value of some jewellery,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">I just show Toby</font>

13:14.416 --> 13:15.936
<font color="#00ffff">what I bought at Tiffany's.</font>

13:17.376 --> 13:19.055
<font color="#00ff00">That's not what you said before.</font>

13:19.056 --> 13:22.055
<font color="#00ff00">You said you were very knowledgeable</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on the Antiques Roadshow.</font>

13:22.056 --> 13:24.815
<font color="#ffff00">So you must've watched it.</font>

13:24.816 --> 13:27.615
<font color="#ffffff">Is there something you're not</font>
<font color="#ffffff">telling us, Anna?</font>

13:27.616 --> 13:30.535
<font color="#ffff00">Who cares what TV programmes</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Anna watches?</font>

13:30.536 --> 13:31.935
<font color="#ffff00">They need to get going!</font>

13:31.936 --> 13:33.255
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, whoa!</font>

13:33.256 --> 13:35.375
<font color="#ffffff">Either somebody's trod something</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in the carpet</font>

13:35.376 --> 13:37.256
<font color="#ffffff">or something smells a bit off to me.</font>

13:40.976 --> 13:42.656
<font color="#00ff00">Well, shit, Sherlock.</font>

13:45.176 --> 13:47.735
<font color="#ffffff">Why are you suddenly in a rush to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">get rid of them?</font>

13:47.736 --> 13:49.815
<font color="#ffffff">What's going on, Lucy?</font>

13:49.816 --> 13:52.656
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, just tell them, Anna.</font>

13:54.536 --> 13:56.815
<font color="#ffffff">Don't tell me you're about to whip</font>
<font color="#ffffff">off your mask and it turns out</font>

13:56.816 --> 13:58.296
<font color="#ffffff">you're Fiona Bruce.</font>

13:59.296 --> 14:02.295
<font color="#00ffff">OK, but this is going to sound</font>
<font color="#00ffff">a little odd. </font><font color="#ffffff">Keep talking.</font>

14:02.296 --> 14:03.775
<font color="#ffffff">I'm used to little and odd.</font>

14:03.776 --> 14:05.415
<font color="#ffffff">Aren't I, Dad?</font>

14:05.416 --> 14:09.495
<font color="#00ffff">Two months ago, my sister did tell</font>
<font color="#00ffff">me the Antiques Roadshow was filming</font>

14:09.496 --> 14:12.415
<font color="#00ffff">in her village. </font><font color="#ffffff">Oh! It's a village</font>
<font color="#ffffff">now, is it? </font><font color="#00ffff">Village, town,</font>

14:12.416 --> 14:13.895
<font color="#00ffff">what's the difference?</font>

14:13.896 --> 14:15.896
<font color="#ffffff">Ipswich Village never won</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the FA Cup.</font>

14:17.536 --> 14:20.615
<font color="#00ffff">She wanted to go on the show but she</font>
<font color="#00ffff">didn't have anything to get valued.</font>

14:20.616 --> 14:22.375
<font color="#00ffff">So she asked me if I had something</font>

14:22.376 --> 14:24.095
<font color="#00ffff">but I couldn't think of anything.</font>

14:24.096 --> 14:26.655
<font color="#ffff00">I'd have thought your house would</font>
<font color="#ffff00">have been full of valuables.</font>

14:26.656 --> 14:28.935
<font color="#00ffff">It is, but we know</font>
<font color="#00ffff">what they're worth.</font>

14:28.936 --> 14:32.015
<font color="#00ffff">What you need to get on that show is</font>
<font color="#00ffff">something that might be valuable</font>

14:32.016 --> 14:34.655
<font color="#00ffff">but also might be worthless tat.</font>

14:34.656 --> 14:36.376
<font color="#00ffff">And that's when I thought of Lucy!</font>

14:38.576 --> 14:40.855
<font color="#00ffff">She mentioned, in passing,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">that that vase</font>

14:40.856 --> 14:42.495
<font color="#00ffff">had been in the family for years.</font>

14:42.496 --> 14:46.175
<font color="#00ffff">And I thought, "Who knows?</font>
<font color="#00ffff">Maybe it's worth something."</font>

14:46.176 --> 14:49.615
<font color="#00ffff">So, I asked if I could take it</font>
<font color="#00ffff">and Lucy seemed very keen.</font>

14:49.616 --> 14:50.935
<font color="#ffffff">Why?</font>

14:50.936 --> 14:53.615
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I just remember Nan saying</font>
<font color="#ffff00">once that she thought</font>

14:53.616 --> 14:55.495
<font color="#ffff00">it might be worth something.</font>

14:55.496 --> 14:58.895
<font color="#ffffff">But you said you only cared about</font>
<font color="#ffffff">its sentimental value. </font><font color="#ffff00">I do.</font>

14:58.896 --> 15:00.615
<font color="#ffff00">That's why I didn't sell it.</font>

15:00.616 --> 15:02.455
<font color="#ffff00">Not even for £2,000.</font>

15:02.456 --> 15:04.615
<font color="#ffffff">I bet you thought about it, though,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">didn't you?</font>

15:04.616 --> 15:08.015
<font color="#ffff00">Thinking about it is not the same as</font>
<font color="#ffff00">actually doing something about it.</font>

15:08.016 --> 15:10.576
<font color="#ffff00">Our broken shed roof is proof of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">that, Lee.</font>

15:12.336 --> 15:14.055
<font color="#ffffff">We could've done with that money.</font>

15:14.056 --> 15:15.095
<font color="#ffff00">What for?</font>

15:15.096 --> 15:16.895
<font color="#ffffff">Well, to start with,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">we need a new vase.</font>

15:16.896 --> 15:18.936
<font color="#ffffff">And, if there's anything left,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a new shed.</font>

15:20.136 --> 15:22.055
<font color="#ffff00">Look, all this was months ago!</font>

15:22.056 --> 15:24.735
<font color="#ffff00">Doesn't get us any closer to finding</font>
<font color="#ffff00">out who broke the damn thing!</font>

15:24.736 --> 15:26.015
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, yes, it does!</font>

15:26.016 --> 15:28.535
<font color="#ffffff">Because, if you're telling us that</font>
<font color="#ffffff">vase on the Antiques Roadshow</font>

15:28.536 --> 15:32.335
<font color="#ffffff">was actually your vase,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">it means it was worth £2,000!</font>

15:32.336 --> 15:36.135
<font color="#ffffff">Which means my original theory</font>
<font color="#ffffff">just might be correct!</font>

15:36.136 --> 15:37.415
<font color="#ffffff">His mate DID undervalue it</font>

15:37.416 --> 15:41.535
<font color="#ffffff">and Dad DID come round this</font>
<font color="#ffffff">afternoon to try and take it!</font>

15:41.536 --> 15:44.215
<font color="#ffff00">There's a word for evidence</font>
<font color="#ffff00">like this.</font>

15:44.216 --> 15:46.255
<font color="#ffff00">Circum...</font>

15:46.256 --> 15:47.496
<font color="#ffff00">..cision.</font>

15:49.336 --> 15:51.815
<font color="#00ffff">I don't think that's the word</font>
<font color="#00ffff">you're looking for.</font>

15:51.816 --> 15:54.056
<font color="#00ff00">Unless you're acting on a tip-off.</font>

15:58.536 --> 16:00.855
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe the Antiques Roadshow valued</font>
<font color="#ffff00">it wrong.</font>

16:00.856 --> 16:02.455
<font color="#ffff00">I've seen that programme.</font>

16:02.456 --> 16:04.855
<font color="#ffff00">It's a lot of nonsense!</font>
<font color="#ffff00">They just make it up!</font>

16:04.856 --> 16:06.295
<font color="#00ffff">No, they don't.</font>

16:06.296 --> 16:07.695
<font color="#ffff00">Don't be stupid.</font>

16:07.696 --> 16:09.135
<font color="#ffff00">Of course they do!</font>

16:09.136 --> 16:11.735
<font color="#ffff00">Everything you see on the</font>
<font color="#ffff00">television's not real, you know.</font>

16:11.736 --> 16:14.415
<font color="#ffff00">I'll bet you're one of these people</font>
<font color="#ffff00">who thinks that Coronation Street's</font>

16:14.416 --> 16:16.495
<font color="#ffff00">a documentary.</font>

16:16.496 --> 16:17.976
<font color="#00ffff">I didn't until I met you.</font>

16:19.416 --> 16:20.975
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, just admit it, Dad!</font>

16:20.976 --> 16:22.455
<font color="#ffffff">You wanted that vase for yourself,</font>

16:22.456 --> 16:25.335
<font color="#ffffff">you accidentally broke it,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and now you're lying.</font>

16:25.336 --> 16:26.775
<font color="#00ff00">Actually...</font>

16:26.776 --> 16:29.175
<font color="#00ff00">..Frank's telling the truth.</font>

16:29.176 --> 16:31.855
<font color="#00ff00">I can't let Frank be accused</font>
<font color="#00ff00">of a crime he didn't commit.</font>

16:31.856 --> 16:33.455
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you, Geoffrey.</font>

16:33.456 --> 16:36.056
<font color="#00ff00">Not when there's such a wealth of</font>
<font color="#00ff00">crimes that he probably did commit.</font>

16:37.656 --> 16:40.295
<font color="#00ff00">Frank's friend didn't undervalue</font>
<font color="#00ff00">that vase, because I happen to know</font>

16:40.296 --> 16:45.495
<font color="#00ff00">for a fact that the vase Wendy took</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to be valued is worth precisely</font>

16:45.496 --> 16:48.255
<font color="#00ff00">£8.99.</font>

16:48.256 --> 16:49.895
<font color="#ffffff">LUCY: </font><font color="#ffff00">Well, how do you know that?</font>

16:49.896 --> 16:51.975
<font color="#00ff00">Because that's how much</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I paid for it yesterday</font>

16:51.976 --> 16:54.095
<font color="#00ff00">at the Hounslow branch...</font>

16:54.096 --> 16:56.295
<font color="#00ff00">..of Bargain Furnishings.</font>

16:56.296 --> 16:58.415
<font color="#ffffff">I think my brain's starting to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">bleed.</font>

16:58.416 --> 17:00.455
<font color="#00ff00">There's a perfectly simple</font>
<font color="#00ff00">explanation.</font>

17:00.456 --> 17:02.535
<font color="#00ff00">After watching the Antiques</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Roadshow,</font>

17:02.536 --> 17:05.655
<font color="#00ff00">I was convinced that Lucy's vase</font>
<font color="#00ff00">was also valuable.</font>

17:05.656 --> 17:07.575
<font color="#00ffff">But that's not what you said!</font>

17:07.576 --> 17:09.935
<font color="#00ffff">You said you thought</font>
<font color="#00ffff">it was a worthless replica!</font>

17:09.935 --> 17:12.375
<font color="#00ff00">I lied. I didn't want you telling</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Lucy because she might have been</font>

17:12.376 --> 17:15.015
<font color="#00ff00">tempted to sell hers. Although, at</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the time, I obviously didn't realise</font>

17:15.016 --> 17:17.974
<font color="#00ff00">that the vase I was looking at</font>
<font color="#00ff00">WAS hers! </font><font color="#00ffff">Why did you lie?!</font>

17:17.976 --> 17:20.335
<font color="#00ff00">Because I wanted it to stay</font>
<font color="#00ff00">in the family!</font>

17:20.336 --> 17:22.295
<font color="#ffff00">I thought you didn't even like</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the vase, Dad.</font>

17:22.296 --> 17:25.015
<font color="#00ff00">Well, it's one thing to dislike</font>
<font color="#00ff00">something and another to want to see</font>

17:25.016 --> 17:27.136
<font color="#00ff00">it removed from the family</font>
<font color="#00ff00">altogether.</font>

17:29.776 --> 17:33.655
<font color="#00ffff">But it's Lucy's decision whether she</font>
<font color="#00ffff">wants to sell the vase, not yours.</font>

17:33.656 --> 17:35.815
<font color="#00ff00">I knew that would be your attitude</font>

17:35.816 --> 17:38.095
<font color="#00ff00">so I decided to play safe and bought</font>

17:38.096 --> 17:40.535
<font color="#00ff00">a substitute vase and then,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">very early this morning,</font>

17:40.536 --> 17:42.455
<font color="#00ff00">before Wendy had even left</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the house,</font>

17:42.456 --> 17:46.695
<font color="#00ff00">I came round here and exchanged</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the original for the replica.</font>

17:46.696 --> 17:49.055
<font color="#ffffff">I don't know why we bother locking</font>
<font color="#ffffff">this door. We should just get</font>

17:49.056 --> 17:50.296
<font color="#ffffff">a revolving one!</font>

17:51.376 --> 17:53.615
<font color="#00ffff">So, the vase I took to be valued</font>

17:53.616 --> 17:54.815
<font color="#00ffff">was a cheap copy.</font>

17:54.816 --> 17:57.735
<font color="#00ff00">Which means my mate didn't</font>
<font color="#00ff00">undervalue it,</font>

17:57.736 --> 18:00.295
<font color="#00ff00">which means I've been vindicated</font>

18:00.296 --> 18:02.495
<font color="#00ff00">and, in case you're wondering, yes,</font>

18:02.496 --> 18:04.096
<font color="#00ff00">I WILL be suing!</font>

18:05.496 --> 18:06.975
<font color="#ffffff">You're right, Dad.</font>

18:06.976 --> 18:08.215
<font color="#ffffff">I'm sorry.</font>

18:08.216 --> 18:09.975
<font color="#ffffff">You didn't try and steal the vase.</font>

18:09.976 --> 18:12.175
<font color="#ffffff">He did!</font>
<font color="#ffffff">And whilst you were round here,</font>

18:12.176 --> 18:14.215
<font color="#ffffff">I'm assuming you accidentally</font>
<font color="#ffffff">smashed it.</font>

18:14.216 --> 18:15.615
<font color="#00ff00">Oh, try and keep up, Lee.</font>

18:15.616 --> 18:18.415
<font color="#00ff00">Of course I didn't break it,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">otherwise Wendy would have nothing</font>

18:18.416 --> 18:20.095
<font color="#00ff00">to take to be valued.</font>

18:20.096 --> 18:21.655
<font color="#ffffff">Oh, yeah.</font>

18:21.656 --> 18:23.495
<font color="#ffffff">I think I need a pen and paper.</font>

18:23.496 --> 18:25.455
<font color="#00ff00">I didn't steal the original, either.</font>

18:25.456 --> 18:27.015
<font color="#00ff00">I just temporarily borrowed it.</font>

18:27.016 --> 18:29.295
<font color="#ffffff">How temporarily?</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Well, what do you mean?</font>

18:29.296 --> 18:30.575
<font color="#ffffff">What I mean...</font>

18:30.576 --> 18:32.935
<font color="#ffffff">..did you come back in later</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and swap them back?</font>

18:32.936 --> 18:37.935
<font color="#ffffff">Because, if you did,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">somebody has broken a £2,000 vase!</font>

18:37.936 --> 18:39.295
<font color="#ffffff">But if you didn't...</font>

18:39.296 --> 18:40.616
<font color="#00ff00">I didn't come back.</font>

18:41.656 --> 18:44.736
<font color="#00ff00">The broken vase is the cheap</font>
<font color="#00ff00">replica.</font>

18:45.976 --> 18:47.216
<font color="#ffff00">Yes! </font><font color="#ffffff">Shed!</font>

18:50.376 --> 18:51.815
<font color="#ffffff">Well?! </font><font color="#00ff00">What?</font>

18:51.816 --> 18:53.855
<font color="#ffffff">Where's our £2,000 vase?</font>

18:53.856 --> 18:56.175
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, it's "ours", now, is it?</font>

18:56.176 --> 18:58.415
<font color="#00ff00">It's in the bag.</font>

18:58.416 --> 19:00.135
<font color="#00ff00">I had intended to swap it back</font>

19:00.136 --> 19:01.935
<font color="#00ff00">in a couple of days after the dust</font>

19:01.936 --> 19:04.935
<font color="#00ff00">had settled but, when I got</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Lee's text telling us to get</font>

19:04.936 --> 19:07.815
<font color="#00ff00">round here urgently, I thought maybe</font>
<font color="#00ff00">you were both getting a bit</font>

19:07.816 --> 19:10.135
<font color="#00ff00">suspicious so, erm, I thought</font>
<font color="#00ff00">I'd try and swap it back</font>

19:10.136 --> 19:12.375
<font color="#00ff00">this evening when no-one was</font>
<font color="#00ff00">looking.</font>

19:12.376 --> 19:13.736
<font color="#ffff00">Tsk, this family.</font>

19:14.936 --> 19:17.015
<font color="#00ff00">When I heard that someone had broken</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the damn thing,</font>

19:17.016 --> 19:19.015
<font color="#00ff00">I could hardly swap it back then,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">could I?</font>

19:19.016 --> 19:22.135
<font color="#00ff00">I mean, what would you have said</font>
<font color="#00ff00">if a broken vase of flowers</font>

19:22.136 --> 19:23.896
<font color="#00ff00">had suddenly reappeared?</font>

19:24.936 --> 19:26.536
<font color="#00ffff">Reincarnation.</font>

19:31.696 --> 19:34.455
<font color="#00ffff">This stuff kills at bridge club.</font>

19:34.456 --> 19:36.935
<font color="#ffff00">Can I have my vase back, then,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">please, Dad?</font>

19:36.936 --> 19:38.695
<font color="#00ff00">How do I know you won't sell it?</font>

19:38.696 --> 19:40.575
<font color="#ffff00">Because I knew it was worth £2,000</font>

19:40.576 --> 19:42.855
<font color="#ffff00">and yet I still didn't sell it,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">did I?</font>

19:42.856 --> 19:44.335
<font color="#00ff00">And what about Lee?</font>

19:44.336 --> 19:47.175
<font color="#ffff00">I don't think I'll be offered £2,000</font>
<font color="#ffff00">for Lee.</font>

19:47.176 --> 19:48.975
<font color="#ffffff">I didn't quite catch that, Lucy?</font>

19:48.976 --> 19:50.935
<font color="#ffffff">Did you say, "Sorry, Lee,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">for accusing you of</font>

19:50.936 --> 19:53.335
<font color="#ffffff">"breaking my nan's vase</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that you clearly didn't break"?</font>

19:53.336 --> 19:54.495
<font color="#ffff00">Sorry.</font>

19:54.496 --> 19:55.695
<font color="#00ffff">Sue her!</font>

19:55.696 --> 19:57.096
<font color="#00ffff">Defecation of character.</font>

19:59.296 --> 20:00.975
<font color="#ffff00">And that's definitely the original</font>
<font color="#ffff00">one?</font>

20:00.976 --> 20:02.296
<font color="#00ff00">Yes.</font>

20:03.296 --> 20:04.415
<font color="#ffffff">How do we know?</font>

20:04.416 --> 20:06.775
<font color="#00ffff">I can get my mate to have a look</font>
<font color="#00ffff">at it, if you like?</font>

20:06.776 --> 20:07.975
<font color="#ffff00">Thanks, Frank,</font>

20:07.976 --> 20:09.896
<font color="#ffff00">but I think we can take</font>
<font color="#ffff00">my dad's word for it.</font>

20:11.216 --> 20:13.375
<font color="#00ff00">So, all's well that ends well.</font>

20:13.376 --> 20:14.935
<font color="#00ff00">Now, can we all please go?</font>

20:14.936 --> 20:16.175
<font color="#ffffff">Er, not quite!</font>

20:16.176 --> 20:19.095
<font color="#ffffff">There's still one important piece of</font>
<font color="#ffffff">the jigsaw missing, isn't there?</font>

20:19.096 --> 20:20.375
<font color="#ffffff">GEOFFREY: </font><font color="#00ff00">Oh, God.</font>

20:20.376 --> 20:21.816
<font color="#00ff00">Hercule's back.</font>

20:22.856 --> 20:25.335
<font color="#ffffff">We still haven't found out</font>
<font color="#ffffff">who broke that vase.</font>

20:25.336 --> 20:26.615
<font color="#00ffff">Who cares?</font>

20:26.616 --> 20:28.135
<font color="#00ffff">It was just a cheap replica.</font>

20:28.136 --> 20:29.455
<font color="#ffffff">I care!</font>

20:29.456 --> 20:32.375
<font color="#ffffff">It's the reason I gathered you</font>
<font color="#ffffff">all round here in the first place.</font>

20:32.376 --> 20:34.735
<font color="#ffffff">Don't worry, you'll all be free to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">leave once we've revealed</font>

20:34.736 --> 20:36.575
<font color="#ffffff">who is the guilty party.</font>

20:36.576 --> 20:38.055
<font color="#ffffff">And it won't take long</font>

20:38.056 --> 20:40.175
<font color="#ffffff">because now I know exactly</font>
<font color="#ffffff">who did it!</font>

20:40.176 --> 20:41.295
<font color="#00ffff">Who?</font>

20:41.296 --> 20:43.375
<font color="#ffffff">Well, at first,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">I thought it was you, Wendy.</font>

20:43.376 --> 20:44.535
<font color="#ffffff">And then Dad.</font>

20:44.536 --> 20:45.615
<font color="#ffffff">And then Anna.</font>

20:45.616 --> 20:48.175
<font color="#ffffff">But I think we've safely ruled out</font>
<font color="#ffffff">you three.</font>

20:48.176 --> 20:50.295
<font color="#ffffff">And then there's Geoffrey,</font>

20:50.296 --> 20:53.375
<font color="#ffffff">a man who swapped the vases</font>
<font color="#ffffff">and claimed</font>

20:53.376 --> 20:55.255
<font color="#ffffff">he never returned.</font>

20:55.256 --> 20:57.575
<font color="#ffffff">But we only have his word for that,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">don't we?</font>

20:57.576 --> 20:59.695
<font color="#ffffff">Did guilt get the better of him?</font>

20:59.696 --> 21:03.215
<font color="#ffffff">Did he in fact return later to</font>
<font color="#ffffff">swap them back and, in the process,</font>

21:03.216 --> 21:04.975
<font color="#ffffff">accidentally break it?</font>

21:04.976 --> 21:06.135
<font color="#00ff00">Well, did I?</font>

21:06.136 --> 21:07.495
<font color="#ffffff">No, you did not.</font>

21:07.496 --> 21:09.775
<font color="#00ff00">Good. Well, I'm glad</font>
<font color="#00ff00">we've established</font>

21:09.776 --> 21:11.856
<font color="#00ff00">that the man who didn't do it</font>
<font color="#00ff00">didn't do it.</font>

21:12.896 --> 21:16.855
<font color="#ffffff">So, just who did lose their grip</font>
<font color="#ffffff">on the family heirloom?</font>

21:16.856 --> 21:18.815
<font color="#ffff00">I'll be getting a grip</font>
<font color="#ffff00">of your family heirlooms</font>

21:18.816 --> 21:20.455
<font color="#ffff00">if you don't get on with it.</font>

21:20.456 --> 21:23.975
<font color="#ffffff">Then there's my beautiful,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">delightful, if somewhat accusatory,</font>

21:23.976 --> 21:25.495
<font color="#ffffff">wife.</font>

21:25.496 --> 21:28.615
<font color="#ffffff">A woman who places so much</font>
<font color="#ffffff">sentimental value on that vase,</font>

21:28.616 --> 21:33.375
<font color="#ffffff">she couldn't bring herself to sell</font>
<font color="#ffffff">it, not even for £2,000.</font>

21:33.376 --> 21:35.375
<font color="#ffffff">But perhaps she could bring herself</font>

21:35.376 --> 21:37.255
<font color="#ffffff">to sneak back in,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">deliberately break it</font>

21:37.256 --> 21:38.976
<font color="#ffffff">and claim on the insurance.</font>

21:40.416 --> 21:42.576
<font color="#ffffff">But don't worry,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that's not what I think happened.</font>

21:44.016 --> 21:46.695
<font color="#ffffff">Hey, having said that,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that's not a bad... </font><font color="#ffff00">No. </font><font color="#ffffff">Right.</font>

21:46.696 --> 21:48.055
<font color="#00ff00">This is so stupid.</font>

21:48.056 --> 21:49.735
<font color="#00ff00">Come on, we're leaving.</font>

21:49.736 --> 21:51.615
<font color="#ffffff">And then finally there's Toby.</font>

21:51.616 --> 21:54.735
<font color="#ffffff">Nothing to do with you, this story,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">is it, Toby?</font>

21:54.736 --> 21:56.775
<font color="#ffffff">Nothing to do with you whatsoever.</font>

21:56.776 --> 21:58.496
<font color="#ffffff">OR SO I THOUGHT!</font>

22:00.096 --> 22:02.775
<font color="#ffffff">And then I started noticing</font>
<font color="#ffffff">a few clues.</font>

22:02.776 --> 22:04.015
<font color="#00ff00">What clues?</font>

22:04.016 --> 22:07.775
<font color="#ffffff">Like the small plaster on the back</font>
<font color="#ffffff">of your hand like a man</font>

22:07.776 --> 22:10.295
<font color="#ffffff">who had recently broken something.</font>

22:10.296 --> 22:12.256
<font color="#00ff00">I cut myself shaving.</font>

22:14.496 --> 22:15.855
<font color="#ffffff">On your knuckles?</font>

22:15.856 --> 22:17.256
<font color="#ffffff">Was it a full moon?</font>

22:18.736 --> 22:21.935
<font color="#ffffff">And then there's the way you just</font>
<font color="#ffffff">moved that fruit bowl for Lucy.</font>

22:21.936 --> 22:24.295
<font color="#ffffff">It told us so much, didn't it?</font>

22:24.296 --> 22:26.696
<font color="#ffffff">Almost like you knew exactly where</font>
<font color="#ffffff">that vase should go.</font>

22:27.896 --> 22:30.455
<font color="#ffffff">And then there's the big one.</font>

22:30.456 --> 22:31.935
<font color="#ffffff">FRANK: </font><font color="#ffff00">Oh, for goodness' sake!</font>

22:31.936 --> 22:33.416
<font color="#ffff00">Not Geoffrey again?!</font>

22:34.736 --> 22:36.055
<font color="#ffff00">We've done him!</font>

22:36.056 --> 22:38.455
<font color="#ffffff">The way you were casually driving</font>

22:38.456 --> 22:40.615
<font color="#ffffff">past this house this afternoon.</font>

22:40.616 --> 22:42.495
<font color="#00ff00">Well, what's wrong with that?</font>

22:42.496 --> 22:44.136
<font color="#ffffff">We live in a cul-de-sac.</font>

22:45.736 --> 22:47.175
<font color="#ffffff">Where were you going exactly?</font>

22:47.176 --> 22:48.616
<font color="#00ff00">To the end.</font>

22:50.896 --> 22:52.895
<font color="#00ff00">And back again.</font>

22:52.896 --> 22:55.415
<font color="#ffffff">I put it to you, ladies and</font>
<font color="#ffffff">gentlemen, that it was in fact</font>

22:55.416 --> 22:59.135
<font color="#ffffff">Toby who sneaked into the house</font>
<font color="#ffffff">today and broke the vase.</font>

22:59.136 --> 23:00.975
<font color="#00ff00">OK, Miss Marple,</font>

23:00.976 --> 23:02.695
<font color="#00ff00">you've got me.</font>

23:02.696 --> 23:04.536
<font color="#ffffff">Stick with Poirot,</font>
<font color="#ffffff">keep it masculine.</font>

23:05.696 --> 23:07.135
<font color="#00ffff">Let's split the difference</font>

23:07.136 --> 23:09.295
<font color="#00ffff">and go with Scooby-Doo.</font>

23:09.296 --> 23:10.535
<font color="#00ff00">You?</font>

23:10.536 --> 23:11.895
<font color="#00ff00">Broke the vase?</font>

23:11.896 --> 23:13.135
<font color="#00ffff">Yes.</font>

23:13.136 --> 23:14.415
<font color="#00ffff">By accident.</font>

23:14.416 --> 23:16.095
<font color="#00ffff">I told you that table was wobbly.</font>

23:16.096 --> 23:18.735
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, you did tell us that,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">didn't you?</font>

23:18.736 --> 23:21.135
<font color="#ffff00">How could you know that unless</font>
<font color="#ffff00">you were the culprit?</font>

23:21.136 --> 23:24.136
<font color="#ffffff">GEOFFREY: </font><font color="#00ff00">He's already admitted it,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Frank, try and keep up!</font>

23:25.256 --> 23:26.695
<font color="#00ffff">But there's one thing missing.</font>

23:26.696 --> 23:29.215
<font color="#00ffff">Toby lacks motivation.</font>

23:29.216 --> 23:30.816
<font color="#00ff00">I've been saying that for years.</font>

23:32.296 --> 23:33.455
<font color="#ffffff">It's a good point.</font>

23:33.456 --> 23:36.575
<font color="#ffffff">What were you doing in this house</font>
<font color="#ffffff">in the first place?</font>

23:36.576 --> 23:39.735
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, look,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">who cares why Toby was here?</font>

23:39.736 --> 23:43.375
<font color="#ffff00">As we all now know, the broken vase</font>
<font color="#ffff00">was just a cheap replica.</font>

23:43.376 --> 23:45.336
<font color="#ffff00">So, why don't we all just get going?</font>

23:48.416 --> 23:50.615
<font color="#00ff00">It's too late, Lucy.</font>

23:50.616 --> 23:52.295
<font color="#00ff00">I think we've been rumbled.</font>

23:52.296 --> 23:54.776
<font color="#00ffff">This story's got more twists</font>
<font color="#00ffff">than a Curly Wurly.</font>

23:56.736 --> 23:59.016
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, just tell them.</font>

24:00.376 --> 24:03.256
<font color="#00ff00">Someone I know is an antiques</font>
<font color="#00ff00">collector.</font>

24:04.256 --> 24:06.615
<font color="#00ff00">Well, he saw Anna's sister</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on the Antiques Roadshow.</font>

24:06.616 --> 24:08.895
<font color="#00ff00">He expressed interest in buying</font>
<font color="#00ff00">the vase.</font>

24:08.896 --> 24:12.735
<font color="#00ff00">So I told Lucy about the interest,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">although I knew she'd already turned</font>

24:12.736 --> 24:17.415
<font color="#00ff00">down £2,000 and probably didn't want</font>
<font color="#00ff00">to sell. </font><font color="#ffff00">And I didn't!</font>

24:17.416 --> 24:18.895
<font color="#00ff00">Until two days ago.</font>

24:18.896 --> 24:21.015
<font color="#ffffff">What happened two days ago?</font>

24:21.016 --> 24:23.655
<font color="#ffff00">Toby's friend offered me £3,000.</font>

24:23.656 --> 24:26.055
<font color="#ffffff">Three grand for that piece of sh...</font>

24:26.056 --> 24:28.615
<font color="#ffffff">..entimentally important artefact?</font>

24:28.616 --> 24:31.055
<font color="#ffffff">What did you say?</font>
<font color="#ffff00">What do you think I said?</font>

24:31.056 --> 24:33.055
<font color="#ffff00">I bit his hand off.</font>

24:33.056 --> 24:34.935
<font color="#ffffff">And were you going to tell me</font>
<font color="#ffffff">about it?!</font>

24:34.936 --> 24:38.495
<font color="#ffff00">No! I couldn't risk Dad finding</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the vase had left the family.</font>

24:38.496 --> 24:42.215
<font color="#00ff00">You'd sell your own grandmother's</font>
<font color="#00ff00">vase for £3,000?</font>

24:42.216 --> 24:43.575
<font color="#ffff00">For £3,000</font>

24:43.576 --> 24:44.856
<font color="#ffff00">I'd sell my own grandmother.</font>

24:45.976 --> 24:47.935
<font color="#ffffff">What about the three grand?</font>
<font color="#ffffff">Were you going to keep</font>

24:47.936 --> 24:50.175
<font color="#ffffff">that a secret from me, too? </font><font color="#ffff00">No.</font>

24:50.176 --> 24:52.775
<font color="#ffff00">I was going to say that a premium</font>
<font color="#ffff00">bond had come up and treat us</font>

24:52.776 --> 24:54.295
<font color="#ffff00">all to a family holiday.</font>

24:54.296 --> 24:56.016
<font color="#ffffff">I wanted a shed!</font>

24:58.456 --> 25:00.855
<font color="#ffff00">I thought you were supposed to</font>
<font color="#ffff00">be coming around tomorrow?!</font>

25:00.856 --> 25:03.295
<font color="#00ff00">I suddenly remembered</font>
<font color="#00ff00">we were visiting Anna's sister</font>

25:03.296 --> 25:05.735
<font color="#00ff00">so I decided to pop round today</font>
<font color="#00ff00">instead.</font>

25:05.736 --> 25:08.895
<font color="#00ff00">I'm sorry. I was going to tell you</font>
<font color="#00ff00">but when I accidentally broke it</font>

25:08.896 --> 25:11.975
<font color="#00ff00">I just sort of panicked and ran.</font>

25:11.976 --> 25:13.615
<font color="#00ffff">When have I seen that before?</font>

25:13.616 --> 25:16.336
<font color="#00ff00">Who doesn't get nervous</font>
<font color="#00ff00">at the altar?!</font>

25:19.896 --> 25:22.215
<font color="#ffffff">And were are you going to confess</font>
<font color="#ffffff">at any point?</font>

25:22.216 --> 25:23.815
<font color="#00ff00">I think you'll find I did!</font>

25:23.816 --> 25:25.775
<font color="#00ff00">Right at the start of all this.</font>

25:25.776 --> 25:27.136
<font color="#00ff00">I said it was me!</font>

